title: Šíp is the only climbable Arrow in the world
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
Anna and Peter talk about hiking Šíp peak, or Arrow peak in English, located in northern Slovakia. It’s time to pack up and seek out an adventure in the hills.  
 
Presenters: Anna Fay, Peter Dlhopolec
